vote.title: Authorize Supplemental Agreement No. 16 to increase the service contract with Tritech Software Systems, for continued maintenance and support of the existing computer aided dispatch system, disaster recovery synchronization, and a computer aided dispatch routing server for the Department of Information and Technology Services - Not to exceed $205,382.69, from $21,069,435.14 to $21,274,817.83 - Financing: 9-1-1 System Operations Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
